      <title>美国货币市场资产升至一个月来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/us-money-market-assets-rise-to-highest-level-in-a-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管最近的经济数据表明美联储今年可能放松货币政策，但由于短期利率上升继续吸引资金，货币市场基金资产有所增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/us-money-market-assets-rise-to-highest-level-in-a-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:30:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>身价超过 1000 亿美元的超级富豪比以往任何时候都多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/more-ultra-rich-are-worth-over-100-billion-than-ever-before</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着人工智能、奢侈品和地缘政治变化的浪潮席卷而来，全球超级富豪俱乐部目前已有 15 名成员，财富超过 1000 亿美元，创下有史以来最高纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/more-ultra-rich-are-worth-over-100-billion-than-ever-before</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:13:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
