      <title>对冲基金在中国寻找便宜货时，大卫·泰珀收购了阿里巴巴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/appaloosa-s-david-tepper-loads-up-on-alibaba-as-hedge-funds-warm-up-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁投资者戴维·泰珀(David Tepper)上个季度买入了遭受重创的中国股票，同时减持了飞速发展的美国科技公司的股份，导致对冲基金经理们在两个市场之间估值差距创纪录的情况下慢慢对中国产生兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/appaloosa-s-david-tepper-loads-up-on-alibaba-as-hedge-funds-warm-up-to-china</guid>
